description: This file initializes a React application by rendering the main App component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It sets up React's strict mode and imports the core React libraries, CSS styles, and the main application component.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components into a DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React elements into the DOM at the specified root.
